<i>that I haven't had time to
kind of mentally prepare myself</i>

38:10.756 --> 38:13.957
<i>to talk to Dr. Now
and do this.</i>

38:15.726 --> 38:19.229
<i>I just hope that he has a plan
for me that can work,</i>

38:19.231 --> 38:22.032
<i>so I can finally lose
the weight.</i>

38:24.902 --> 38:26.670
Mr. McNeill.

38:26.672 --> 38:28.605
<i>I know that I have a lot
to lose,</i>

38:28.607 --> 38:30.840
<i>no matter what
