45:13.878 --> 45:17.113
So I know the struggles but...

45:17.948 --> 45:20.516
So everybody look like
they know what to do.

45:20.518 --> 45:22.585
- Right.
- But not for Paul.

45:22.587 --> 45:27.390
So let's keep Paul happy and
give him more... whatever he want.

45:27.392 --> 45:29.525
Instead of making
him permanently happy

45:29.527 --> 45:32.695
we try to make him happy
in that moment. But, yeah.

45:32.697 --> 45:35.998
We know it's not good
and we have to change.

45:36.000 --> 45:39.102
So this is all more reason
you need to be here

45:39.104 --> 45:43.973
so we can get you to be accountable
for your eating habit, okay?

45:44.174 --> 45:45.007
Yes, sir.

45:45.009 --> 45:46.943
But until then,
you need to realize that

45:46.945 --> 45:49.679
enabling people
are gonna be around you,

45:49.681 --> 45:52.381
but ultimately it is
your responsibility

45:52.383 --> 45:53.449
to change your eating habit.

